Package: pathways
Type: Package
Title: A 'Shiny' Application for Exploring the Pathways Corpus
Version: 1.0.3
Date: 2024-06-21
Authors@R: person("Carsten", "Schwemmer", email = "c.schwem2er@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9084-946X"), role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/cschwem2er/pathways
BugReports: https://github.com/cschwem2er/pathways/issues
Description: This app enables interactive exploration of the Pathways Corpus for studying the political representation of Citizens of Immigrant Origin. It includes parliamentary written questions from democracies of eight European countries: Belgium, France, Germany, Greece, Italy, Netherlands, Spain, and the United Kingdom.
